OL,5, A promotional video for Yorkshire Water
OL,6, has been criticised for using stock    
OL,7, footage of the rolling hills of        
OL,8, Herefordshire and images taken in a    
OL,9, Russian bar.                           
OL,11,FThe advert was meant to promote the    
OL,12,FBradford-based company's campaign      
OL,13,Furging customers to save water.        
OL,15,FBut viewers took to social media to    
OL,16,Fpoint out the errors, with one branding
OL,17,Fthe ad "more Malvern than Malton".     
OL,19,FYorkshire Water said the advert had    
OL,20,Fsince been removed from its channels.  
